Launceston Flood Risk Management Order 2023

I make the following order under section 4(1) of the Launceston Flood Risk Management Act 2015 .

20 February 2023

Nic Street

Minister for Local Government

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Launceston Flood Risk Management Order 2023 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect on the day on which its making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Act
    In this order, the Launceston Flood Risk Management Act 2015 is referred to as the Principal Act.

4.
    The amendment effected by this clause has been incorporated into the authorised version of the Launceston Flood Risk Management Act 2015 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 1 March 2023

This order is administered in the Department of Natural Resources and Environment Tasmania.
